mutation ($payload:AdminCreateLangInput!)
{
	adminCreateLang (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	adminGetLangs (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	adminFindLang (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	adminFindLangById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:AdminUpdateLangInput!)
{
	adminUpdateLang (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	adminDeleteLangById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{

	{

		name
		image
		iso6392

		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
